comments.text: The writing in this special is solid. Well worth the hype. The character development for Bartleby, Knuckles, Athair, and Delphius was well done and perfectly executed. Bartleby teaching Sonic about self acceptance and that there's nothing wrong with his weakness as his friends will provide their own strength, talent, and support. A good lesson for the viewers as it shows the importance of bonds and trust in frienship. This was an amazing and serious story.
